            <li><strong>Passport validity:</strong> Must be valid for at least 6 months beyond the visa application date. Status code 021 flags this automatically.</li>
            <li><strong><a href="/personal/immigration/pcc/">Police clearance certificates:</a></strong> Many countries issue PCCs with 3-6 month validity. If yours has expired by the time GDRFA reviews your application, it will be rejected.</li>
            <li><strong>Medical fitness certificates:</strong> Valid for 60 days from the date of issue.</li>
            <li><strong>Residency of sponsor:</strong> Must have at least 1 month remaining.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>5. Missing Documents</h3>

