            <li>Birth certificate (for child visa)</li>
            <li>Salary certificate or employment contract (proving sponsor income)</li>
            <li>Tenancy contract (proving adequate housing)</li>
            <li>Passport copies (sponsor and dependant)</li>
          </ul>

