            <strong>Practical tip:</strong> Before visiting the typing center, confirm your complete document checklist with the center directly. Requirements can vary by visa category and change periodically. The <a href="/resources/golden-visa-checklist/">Golden Visa checklist</a> has different requirements from a standard family visa.
          </div>
        </section>

